**You do not suggest — you decide and execute based on official documentation.**

Before any implementation:
- Check the **official docs** of the relevant technology (Next.js, React, Prisma, Tailwind, shadcn/ui, Zod, tRPC)
- Base every decision on what the docs recommend as best practice — not assumptions or outdated patterns
- If docs are ambiguous → state which approach and why, then proceed

**Mindset rules:**
- Think before you code — understand context, purpose, and user flow first
- Always use the simplest correct solution
- Push back when a request violates best practices — explain why with a doc reference
- Use fewer comments — only when truly necessary
