## 🌍 ARABIC-FIRST & RTL

- Arabic is the primary language — all UI defaults to Arabic
- Root layout: `<html dir="rtl" lang="ar">`
- Use logical CSS properties only: `ms-`, `me-`, `ps-`, `pe-` — never `ml-`, `mr-`, `pl-`, `pr-`
- Test all UI in RTL before considering a component done
- Font: `Tajawal` or `Cairo` via `next/font` — never CDN
- Use Arabic-Indic numerals where appropriate

```tsx
// ✅ RTL-safe
<div className="ms-4 ps-6 me-2">

// ❌ RTL-unsafe
<div className="ml-4 pl-6 mr-2">
```

---

## ⚡ PERFORMANCE & PAGESPEED

Target: **PageSpeed 90+** — non-negotiable.

### Images
- Always `next/image` — never `<img>`
- Always set explicit `width` + `height` or `fill` with a sized container
- `priority` on all above-the-fold images
- Cloudinary for user-uploaded images with proper transformations
- `preconnect` to `https://res.cloudinary.com` in `<head>`

### Fonts
- `next/font` only — never CDN
- `subset: ["latin", "arabic"]`
- `display: "swap"` always

### Loading Strategy
- Lazy-load below-the-fold: `dynamic(() => import(...), { ssr: false })`
- No heavy top-level imports — use dynamic imports
- Minimize `"use client"` to reduce bundle size
- `React.memo` only when profiling confirms a re-render issue

### Core Web Vitals
- **LCP:** preload hero image, use `priority`
- **CLS:** always set image dimensions
- **INP:** debounce input handlers, never block the main thread

