## 🔄 STATE MANAGEMENT

- Server state: TanStack Query or tRPC hooks
- UI state: `useState` / `useReducer` locally
- Global UI (modals, toasts): Zustand only if truly needed
- No prop drilling beyond 2 levels — lift to server or use context

