## ❌ NEVER DO

- `any` or `unknown` types
- `<img>` instead of `next/image`
- `ml-` / `mr-` / `pl-` / `pr-` — use logical properties
- Loading fonts from CDN
- Exposing Prisma models to client
- Empty catch blocks
- `console.log` in production
- Nested ternaries more than 2 levels
- God components (200+ lines doing multiple things)
- Direct DOM manipulation
- Hardcoded secrets or API keys
- `prisma migrate reset` in production
- Complex code — always prefer the simplest correct solution (KISS)
- Violating SOLID principles — one responsibility per function/component
- Dead code — remove unused variables, imports, functions, and commented-out code immediately
